attributes.description: Overview of Datastore logs in Cyera.

params.markdown:
This dashboard provides visibility into datastore objects identified within Cyera.

This dashboard provides overview of issues inside datastore objects that are open, closed and in progress. It highlights trends of datastores over time, cloud providers, type, and sensitivity, regions, as well as owners and public accessibility tied to risks. A essential details view present datastore-level context to support faster triage, compliance alignment, and effective remediation.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/cyera/overview)**
